# Title: Okta API Token Created
# Author: Austin Songer @austinsonger
# Date: 2021-09-12
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when a API token is created
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/identity/okta/okta_api_token_created.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate creation of an API token by authorized users

eventtype="system.api_token.create"